Loader` to use its fallback `ClassLoader#loadClass(...)` path.\\n\\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests.\\n\\nNote: `metadata/org.apache.seata/seata-all/2.1.0/` remains untracked and was not included in the commit.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0c04ed5c52a4d0580169f178dd02e481a3b33ee6f4b03e5563\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 553, \"output\": 246, \"cacheRead\": 32256, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 33055, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777432793371, \"responseId\": \"resp_0c04ed5c52a4d0580169f178da066081a39fef5cb7312b1c56\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.apache.seata:seata-all:2.1.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T03-12-23-636048Z.log:41:  - After finishing this generation, create a git commit with a focused message describing the test changes.\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.apache.seata:seata-all:2.1.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T03-12-23-636048Z.log:51:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Role: You are an expert JVM test engineer specializing in high-coverage integration testing for external libraries.\\n\\nTask:\\nImprove test coverage for the active dynamic-access class in `org.apache.seata:seata-all:2.1.0`.\\n\\nSource Context:\\nCoordinate: org.apache.seata:seata-all:2.1.0\\nRepository URL: https://github.com/apache/incubator-seata\\nMain sources:\\n- URL: https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/seata/seata-all/2.1.0/seata-all-2.1.0-sources.jar\\n- Local path: local_repositories/source_context/org.apache.seata/seata-all/2.1.0/main\\n- Files available: 1116\\n\\nActive class:\\n- Class: org.apache.seata.spring.annotation.GlobalTransactionScanner\\n- Source file: /hom